children.name: Look for videos and case studies which capture the parent mela or parent meeting conducted in different schools. Focus on the ideas being used and themes being selected.

tasks.name: Look for samples of parent mela/ excitement building parent meeting from different schools

children.name: -Meeting with teachers to discuss the importance and role of parent mela in improving community engagement in the school.
- Form a committee among teachers to plan and facilitate the mela along with the school leader.

tasks.name: Form a parent mela committee among the teachers

children.name:
Finalize the themes and activities for the mela. This could be taken borrowed from other schools or decided by the teachers through brainstorming. 
Finalize the dates for the same
Communicate the event with parents and invite them to the mela
Do necessary arrangements for smooth functioning of the event and to make it attractive and interesting to parents
Make sure you collect feedback from parents after the event and reflect among the teachers to see the areas of improvement for next year.
